ねっ ３人とも怪しいよね

138
00:10:39.347 --> 00:10:40.973 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（ケンヤ）きょうも
独りぼっちだな

139
00:10:41.057 --> 00:10:42.475 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
どうする？

140
00:10:43.601 --> 00:10:46.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）変なやつだって
思われてもいい

141
00:10:46.854 --> 00:10:48.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
声 掛けてみよう

142
00:10:49.106 --> 00:10:50.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）手遅れになる前に―

143
00:10:50.900 --> 00:10:53.194 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ただ 真剣に向かい合えばいい

144
00:10:58.658 --> 00:11:00.076 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）こんにちは

145
00:11:00.493 --> 00:11:03.746 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
俺 美琴(みこと)小５年の 藤沼(ふじぬま) 悟

146
00:11:04.288 --> 00:11:07.833 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
中西 彩さん… だよね？

147
00:11:08.876 --> 00:11:10.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（彩）どっかで会ったっけ？

148
00:11:10.795 --> 00:11:11.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
いや…

149
00:11:15.549 --> 00:11:18.386 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ねえ その本 何 読んでんの？

150
00:11:18.511 --> 00:11:20.054 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
俺も 読書が好きで

151
00:11:20.513 --> 00:11:23.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
ウィリアム･シェイクスピアの
「キング リア」

152
00:11:23.933 --> 00:11:25.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
「リア王」…

153
00:11:25.768 --> 00:11:30.022 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
ず… ずいぶん難しい本
読んでるんだね

154
00:11:30.815 --> 00:11:32.650 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あっ 思い出した

155
00:11:32.775 --> 00:11:35.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
あんたら あの川の
向こうの建物に―

156
00:11:35.444 --> 00:11:37.613 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
よく忍び込んでる子たちだべ

157
00:11:37.696 --> 00:11:39.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
アジト…

158
00:11:39.615 --> 00:11:42.201 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
対岸からだと丸見えなのか…

159
00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:44.286 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（彩）アジト？

160
00:11:45.329 --> 00:11:47.832 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
やっぱり男子って 子どもっぽい

161
00:11:49.750 --> 00:11:50.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
じゃ 塾だから

162
00:11:51.585 --> 00:11:52.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（カズ）待て！

163
00:11:56.632 --> 00:11:58.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
アジトは男のロマンだ！

164
00:11:59.009 --> 00:12:00.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
暇なら来てみれや

165
00:12:01.220 --> 00:12:03.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
そうすりゃ 分かる
（オサム）い いてっ

166
00:12:04.598 --> 00:12:08.018 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（彩）そんなことして
何 楽しいんだべか

167
00:12:08.394 --> 00:12:10.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
変な人たち

168
00:12:12.314 --> 00:12:14.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）完璧に しくじった…

169
00:12:14.650 --> 00:12:16.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟･ケンヤ）ハァ…

170
00:12:23.868 --> 00:12:26.287 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）独りぼっちに
しないってだけなのに―

171
00:12:26.537 --> 00:12:28.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
こんなに難しいなんて…

172
00:12:29.248 --> 00:12:30.666 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（加代）悟！

173
00:12:35.838 --> 00:12:41.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
♪～

174
00:12:54.482 --> 00:12:55.983 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（加代）バカなの？

175
00:13:06.911 --> 00:13:13.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（板書する音）

176
00:13:13.626 --> 00:13:14.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（八代）
おととい実験したように―

177
00:13:15.085 --> 00:13:18.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
虫眼鏡のように
真ん中が膨らんでいて…

178
00:13:18.380 --> 00:13:20.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）加代が帰ってきた

179
00:13:20.799 --> 00:13:24.970 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
おばあちゃんの家から バスで
通学することが許可されたそうだ

180
00:13:25.095 --> 00:13:29.725 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
全部 八代先生が動いてくれたと
加代は言っていた

181
00:13:30.726 --> 00:13:33.062 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（八代）これを“焦点”という

182
00:13:38.526 --> 00:13:41.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）いてっ
（児童たち）ハハハ…

183
00:13:41.570 --> 00:13:44.073 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
フッ ハハハ…

184
00:13:44.198 --> 00:13:47.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
そして このレンズの中心から
焦点までの距離―

185
00:13:47.535 --> 00:13:49.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
これを“焦点距離”という

186
00:13:53.207 --> 00:13:55.709 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（オサム）カズ
最近 アジト 行ってないべ？

187
00:13:55.834 --> 00:13:57.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（カズ）したっけ 行くべ
（オサム）うん

188
00:13:57.711 --> 00:13:59.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（カズ）なあ 悟 アジト寄るべ

189
00:13:59.755 --> 00:14:01.048 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
雛月(ひなづき)も連れてさ

190
00:14:01.632 --> 00:14:02.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
アジト…

191
00:14:04.969 --> 00:14:06.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）そういえば―

192
00:14:06.679 --> 00:14:09.557 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
リバイバルしてから
一度も アジトに行ってない

193
00:14:24.113 --> 00:14:26.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）１度目の昭和63年では―

194
00:14:28.659 --> 00:14:31.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
あそこで ヒロミの遺体が
発見されたけど…

195
00:14:33.622 --> 00:14:36.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（加代とヒロミの話し声）

196
00:14:36.959 --> 00:14:38.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）今のままなら―

197
00:14:38.627 --> 00:14:41.297 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
アジトは 事件とは無縁のはずだ

198
00:14:42.131 --> 00:14:45.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
うん いい考えだね 行くべ

199
00:14:46.051 --> 00:14:47.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（カズ）みんな アジト 寄るべ

200
00:14:47.761 --> 00:14:49.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
雛月も 一緒 行くべ！

201
00:14:49.263 --> 00:14:50.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（ケンヤ）ああ

202
00:15:07.197 --> 00:15:13.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
♪～

203
00:15:35.601 --> 00:15:36.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）よしっ

204
00:15:36.977 --> 00:15:39.355 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
悟って こういうとこ 好きだね

205
00:15:39.480 --> 00:15:41.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
男子は みんなさ

206
00:15:41.941 --> 00:15:43.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（ヒロミ）悟君
（悟）何？

207
00:15:43.609 --> 00:15:45.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（ヒロミ）そろそろ
４時になるけど

208
00:15:45.486 --> 00:15:46.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）うん 大丈夫

209
00:15:47.112 --> 00:15:50.074 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
ほら 灯台の様子なら
こっからでも見えるし

210
00:15:55.621 --> 00:15:57.164 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
まだ 来てないや

211
00:15:57.414 --> 00:15:58.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）そっか

212
00:16:01.710 --> 00:16:03.045 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（ノック）

213
00:16:03.796 --> 00:16:04.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（カズ）誰？

214
00:16:08.425 --> 00:16:11.220 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（彩）アジト 暇だから来てみたわ

215
00:16:11.345 --> 00:16:13.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
俺らのアジトへ ようこそ

216
00:16:13.681 --> 00:16:14.765 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
入れ 入れ

217
00:16:14.848 --> 00:16:16.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
オサム お前どけ

218
00:16:16.350 --> 00:16:19.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
えっ 何でよ もう…
（彩）お邪魔します

219
00:16:19.770 --> 00:16:21.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（カズ）オセロするべ
（彩）うん

220
00:16:21.271 --> 00:16:23.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（カズ）俺 なまら強いんだ

221
00:16:23.649 --> 00:16:27.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（彩）よろしくお願いします
（カズ）よろしくお願いします

222
00:16:30.364 --> 00:16:32.533 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（ヒロミ）上がり！
（悟）ああっ

223
00:16:35.285 --> 00:16:36.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟･ヒロミ）ハハハッ！

224
00:16:43.293 --> 00:16:45.087 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（カズ）好きな遊びは？

225
00:16:45.421 --> 00:16:47.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
うーん スケート

226
00:16:50.801 --> 00:16:53.178 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（カズ）ああ 負けた
（彩）やった

227
00:16:53.303 --> 00:16:55.848 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（ケンヤ）子どもっぽさを
突き抜けた男っぽさに―

228
00:16:55.973 --> 00:16:58.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ひかれたっつうことか

229
00:16:58.559 --> 00:17:00.269 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あの様子だと―

230
00:17:00.894 --> 00:17:02.104 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
カズもね

231
00:17:03.022 --> 00:17:04.732 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）予想外の展開で―

232
00:17:04.857 --> 00:17:08.193 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
中西 彩の独りぼっちの時間は
埋められそうだ

233
00:17:12.364 --> 00:17:15.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
それで 探偵ごっこは？

234
00:17:15.325 --> 00:17:16.827 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
これで終わるつもりか？

235
00:17:17.453 --> 00:17:18.495 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
いや

236
00:17:19.038 --> 00:17:20.998 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
まだ終わってたまるか

237
00:17:29.673 --> 00:17:31.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（女子児童）美里(みさと)って
ホントやだよね

238
00:17:31.759 --> 00:17:34.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（女子児童たち）
だよね？ 分かる それ～！

239
00:17:34.970 --> 00:17:38.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
わあ～ やだやだ！

240
00:17:40.768 --> 00:17:41.810 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）加代

241
00:17:43.312 --> 00:17:45.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
きょう 科学館 行かない？

242
00:17:48.942 --> 00:17:51.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
その前に 寄りたいとこ
あるんだけど いい？

243
00:17:51.570 --> 00:17:52.988 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
えっ？

244
00:18:01.330 --> 00:18:03.082 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）昼間に見ると―

245
00:18:03.165 --> 00:18:05.542 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ただのハゲた木だなあ

246
00:18:07.920 --> 00:18:09.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
バカなの？

247
00:18:10.714 --> 00:18:12.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）待ってよ

248
00:18:19.431 --> 00:18:23.227 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
悟に ちゃんと
言ってなかったことがあるんだ

249
00:18:23.352 --> 00:18:25.771 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）な… 何？

250
00:18:33.862 --> 00:18:35.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ありがとう

251
00:18:36.865 --> 00:18:39.451 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あの場所から連れ出してくれて

252
00:18:43.330 --> 00:18:44.790 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
悟は…

253
00:18:46.917 --> 00:18:48.752 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
私のヒーローだよ

254
00:18:54.758 --> 00:18:55.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
何か言え！

255
00:18:58.345 --> 00:18:59.388 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）ほっ

256
00:19:07.896 --> 00:19:08.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）ほっ

257
00:19:09.898 --> 00:19:11.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
待て…

258
00:19:12.276 --> 00:19:16.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）今 俺がしているのは
決して むだじゃない

259
00:19:16.905 --> 00:19:18.907 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
本気で そう思えた

260
00:19:29.501 --> 00:19:31.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（加代）そういえばさ 悟

261
00:19:32.171 --> 00:19:34.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
美里 独りぼっちなの
気付いてた？

262
00:19:34.965 --> 00:19:36.091 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）えっ…

263
00:19:36.216 --> 00:19:39.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あの 給食費の件からかな？

264
00:19:43.599 --> 00:19:45.225 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（加代）ちょっと 気になる

265
00:19:46.185 --> 00:19:49.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）分かった 月曜日に
声 掛けてみようよ

266
00:19:58.780 --> 00:20:02.534 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
（悟）ただいま
（佐知子）おかえり こたつ入りな

267
00:20:07.039 --> 00:20:08.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（澤田(さわだ)）こんにちは

268
00:20:08.415 --> 00:20:10.500 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
テレビ石狩(いしかり)で記者をしている
澤田です

269
00:20:10.626 --> 00:20:13.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
お母さんの知り合いで
ちょっと話を聞きに来たんだ

270
00:20:14.504 --> 00:20:17.049 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
あっ 初めまして

271
00:20:17.174 --> 00:20:18.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（澤田）初めまして

272
00:20:22.221 --> 00:20:24.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（佐知子）なんだべ この子

273
00:20:28.644 --> 00:20:29.770 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
ハハッ…

274
00:20:33.440 --> 00:20:34.608 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）あの…

275
00:20:36.318 --> 00:20:40.739 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
僕も一緒に
話を聞いていいですか？

276
00:20:42.324 --> 00:20:43.992 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
悟 あんた―

277
00:20:44.117 --> 00:20:46.411 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
